{"tid":631277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極大爭議】自己撳掣結束生命 荷蘭展出「自殺膠囊艙」","createTime":"2018-04-16T10:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T11:18:41.000Z","uid":2719,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b77460e575633e9016a6c2f0dac1b5f173fc491f","tid":631277,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/181900_ab83c5e5ce287414b18a252d81f0b562.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F181900_ab83c5e5ce287414b18a252d81f0b562.png&h=84329c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭阿姆斯特丹舉辦殯儀展，展場有一個外形如豆莢容器，引來圍觀兼體驗，它並非普通棺材，而是「自殺機」，只要躺在莢裏，按掣就會釋出氮氣，就此一命嗚呼。<br />\n<br />\n這個3D打印的「Sarco」（石棺的簡稱），是澳洲爭取安藥死權利人士尼奇克與荷蘭設計師班寧克的合作成果。尼奇克介紹說：「Sarco是為一心求死的人而設，一按掣，艙裏就會充斥氮氣，你會略感暈眩，但很快就會失去知覺，撒手塵寰。」<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭早在2002年把安樂死合法化，對病重者尋求解脫，態度開明，但助人尋短見是另一回事。尼奇克卻認為，尋死「並非病入膏肓者特權，而是基本人權」。「在許多地方自殺並不犯法&hellip;&hellip;尋死的人只是不選擇跳軌、而是按掣罷了。」兩人表示希望今年製成首個可運作的Sarco，把設計圖公開任人下載。<br />\n<br />\n兩人預備一副VR眼鏡，讓參觀者體驗置身艙內「找死」感覺。52歲的皮特或會「死過返尋味」，讚道：「古怪的體驗&hellip;&hellip;有月亮有大海，很平靜很悅目。」同樣是52歲的羅布卻不屑一顧：「這東西太蠢了。我沒有興趣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180415/58074950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F58074950&d=0955fzHkKFo8gU5cknr%2BF8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=35de8daf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F58074950&h=1f83afa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180415/58074950</a>"},{"pid":"e4b76dd31e3096c660439e9605b0bddcc6d2c0d0","tid":631277,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:22:43.000Z","msg":"呃d嘈到仆街既人入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab95577c0c9f038c9dce8d0ee3cf62298bf1b28","tid":631277,"uid":71864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"設計圖任人下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5817f564e44b1234c43767f79c9083302b2a43","tid":631277,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:36:18.000Z","msg":"好想入去訓低襟掣"},{"pid":"2ebae55f18dfe836b814a8a35830848fcc338697","tid":631277,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"從文字睇好似無乜痛楚<br />\n香港合法應該有一半人參加"},{"pid":"9751ad0f2f1da351e4ffe0e1ff84f9a2699eab0c","tid":631277,"uid":35129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ebae55f18dfe836b814a8a35830848fcc338697","tid":631277,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"從文字睇好似無乜痛楚<br />\n香港合法應該有一半人參加"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"一半咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92aac65ce046ff024a730f2c155f6f8671a09cf","tid":631277,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9751ad0f2f1da351e4ffe0e1ff84f9a2699eab0c","tid":631277,"uid":35129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ebae55f18dfe836b814a8a35830848fcc338697","tid":631277,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"從文字睇好似無乜痛楚<br />\n香港合法應該有一半人參加"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"一半咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"我係到諗<br />\n跳樓咁恐怖都咁多學生跳<br />\n呢個如果合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041f246fbc8c75d2595e396a37398a827ac3bbfd","tid":631277,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"好CHILL"}]}